    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-01-21T19:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-01-21T19:00:00-05:00" n="249"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d249">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 657.119/257b</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Norway</hi> (<persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_SAG1"
                        type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schmedeman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-01-21T19:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 21, 1918—7 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>210. Please inform the Norwegian Government that the War Trade Board is
                    considering making public in American newspapers <pb facs="0281" n="1115"
                        xml:id="pg_1115"/> not earlier than morning of Thursday the 24th its last
                    proposal for rationing agreement which includes a complete rationing list. This
                    action is taken in order that the American people may know of the fair and
                    reasonable proposals made by the War Trade Board to the Norwegian
                    Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_PFL1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
